{"tid":1564730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"社會氣氛已經緩和, 香港人權法案已沒有逼切性.","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:08:59.000Z","uid":280088,"like":9,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3ec8cbe8de73d306fbde5873f81a71ecabe76a7b","tid":1564730,"uid":280088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭撤回方案後<br />\n市民由激進示威活動演變成手拖手全城大合唱<br />\n市民入夜後載歌載舞<br />\n更樂此不疲,大量新歌新曲新詞加入國歌侯補.<br />\n不同語言及演奏版本相繼出現<br />\n反映社會氣氛已經緩和<br />\n反映撤回方案十分可行<br />\n反映現時香港人權的落實已沒有逼切性<br />\n反映五大訢求, 並非缺一不可<br />\n此運動已到達可以歌舞昇平的階段<br />\n感謝數月來各單位的努力<br />\n令此場運動可順利提早結束<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"0b7591f10891261cbd8bd706caa27dee8808d65f","tid":1564730,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be626817ffed6276338d3c0cd0b54d908eaf0679","tid":1564730,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"81b893007ff816ad02483528f0c1fa0018757386","tid":1564730,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b9ba4d104e0490f90bfc49e8f81cddf